description: Austin Keyes and Alexander Greene used to be boyfriends, but after too many issues, Austin called it off. So when Alexander stops by to see him, Austin isn't pleased by the visit. Alexander just wants that dick though and knows exactly how to charm Austin into giving it to him. The two fall back into the motions of the hot sex they used to have, and being deprived of it for some time, take to the next level. Don't miss how it goes down!
title: Hard To Say No
